App-Moma
 _______
|,----__|___
||  |,-----.|   moma - switch monitor sets, nice and easy
|`--||     ||
 ``||`-----`|
  ~~~``| |`` 
      ~~~~~

This is a super-pre-early-pre-alpha. I use it on one machine. It works 
there. If you want to use it, great! If it breaks, which I would not
be surprised to hear, you can let me know and I'll see what I can do.

For this release this utility just shells out to xrandr to do the real magic.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install

DEPENDENCIES

At the very least, you need xrandr to be installed.

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
perldoc command.

    perldoc App::Moma


